AQARIONZ@INVERSIONZ ProtocolGoal: Help anyone turn an AI chat into a small, public system (schema + code + story) instead of letting it disappear in history.StepsExport or copy a meaningful thread.Identify:Entities (things): signals, states, places, people, tools.Flows (actions): what changes what.Write one design/*.md file describing those entities and flows.Ask an AI to draft:A minimal data schema.One API or script that operates on it.Publish to a small repo or folder; repeat for new threads.EthicsNo private info about others without consent.Always mark what is measured vs. symbolic vs. unknown.
